Modifications (per Apache-2.0 §4(b))
------------------------------------
Forked into the ieidev-team plugin on 2026-06-19. Changes relative to the
original SKILL.md:

1. Frontmatter `name` is kept as `frontend-design`, identical to upstream.
   The fork coexists with / replaces the upstream skill within the ieidev-team
   cluster purely by its plugin namespace: it is referenced as
   `ieidev-team:frontend-design`, distinct from upstream
   `frontend-design:frontend-design`. (Fork identity is carried by this NOTICE
   plus the namespace, not by a name prefix.)
2. Frontmatter `license` field updated to point at the bundled LICENSE/NOTICE.
3. This provenance NOTICE added (and a short notice comment in SKILL.md).

The design-methodology body of SKILL.md is retained verbatim from the original;
no methodology guidance was altered.

Rationale
---------
The ieidev-team clean-room cluster removes runtime dependencies on third-party
plugins. The req-architect prototype agent (`req-architect-prototype`) now calls
`ieidev-team:frontend-design` instead of `frontend-design:frontend-design`.

The Apache-2.0 LICENSE of the original work is retained unmodified in ./LICENSE.
